{"tid":2506030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：世衛將於兩星期內決定是否認可科興疫苗 如獲授將可出口數百萬支到國外","createTime":"2021-04-27T05:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T05:48:09.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c447fadf0120c0138c3510900ee124d1ba9899a","tid":2506030,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"世衛助理總幹事 Mari&acirc;ngela Sim&atilde;o 周一 (26/4) 在例行會議上指，世衛將在未來兩周內決定是否緊急批准由國藥與科興生物研發的兩款中國武漢肺炎 (COVID-10) 疫苗，一旦獲批將是首次有西方國家以外研發的疫苗，獲世衛的認可&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如獲得授權，該兩款疫苗將納入世衞主導的全球疫苗接種計劃 (COVAX) ，可向貧窮國家提供抗疫。中國已在國內部署了該兩款數以百萬計的疫苗，將它們出口到許多國家，當中包括拉丁美洲和非洲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4111794205572835/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4111794205572835%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=69435451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4111794205572835/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d83dc7ebcc7706dd3ef070fc5c1b0d709bbfa9e1","tid":2506030,"uid":89182,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"Cctoy：每枝疫苗都植入左監控技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藉此控制其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c16b0eb35909685f308b57e22c2950cceecdd96","tid":2506030,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"好呀，定外面國家都以為科興有用，之後繼續爆"},{"pid":"dc289088a83f6bdb6ac417ba2ec2f62182d6b787","tid":2506030,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83dc7ebcc7706dd3ef070fc5c1b0d709bbfa9e1","tid":2506030,"uid":89182,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"Cctoy：每枝疫苗都植入左監控技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藉此控制其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"